name: [one-build]
body:
- [one-import-tf] : command line tool to convert TensorFlow to circle
- [one-import-tflite] : command line tool to convert TensorFlow lite to circle
- [one-import-onnx] : command line tool to convert ONNX to circle
- [one-import-bcq] : command line tool to convert TensorFlow with BCQ to circle
description: command line tool to run ONE drivers in customized order

name: [one-import-tf]
body:
- input_path : full filepath of the input file
- output_path : full filepath of the output file
- input_arrays : names of the input arrays, comma-separated
- input_shapes : shapes corresponding to --input_arrays, colon-separated (ex:"1,4,4,3:1,20,20,3")
- output_arrays : names of the output arrays, comma-separated
- converter_version : use TensorFlow Lite Converter version
	- v1 : use TensorFlow Lite Converter 1.x
	- v2 : use TensorFlow Lite Converter 2.x
- save_intermediate : Save intermediate files to output folder
- model_format
	- graph_def : use graph def file(default)
	- saved_model : use saved model
	- keras_model : use keras model
description: command line tool to convert TensorFlow to circle
